sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant EnvoyGW as Envoy Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant vLLMMetrics as vLLM Metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP
    participant Encoder as Remote Encoder<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Inference Request Scheduling (EPP)
    Client->>EnvoyGW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
    EnvoyGW->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC streaming, TLS (self-signed)
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pod, Objectives<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: CRD state updates
    EPP->>vLLMMetrics: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, InsecureSkipVerify
    vLLMMetrics-->>EPP: queue_depth, kv_cache_util, running_requests
    Note over EPP: Filter → Score → Pick pipeline<br/>(KV cache, load, session affinity)
    EPP-->>EnvoyGW: ProcessingResponse<br/>target endpoint + headers
    EnvoyGW->>Decoder: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS

    Note over Client,Encoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (Sidecar P/D)
    EnvoyGW->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Note over Sidecar: Validate prefill target<br/>against SSRF allowlist
    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill result + KV cache params
    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/completions<br/>with KV cache reference<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming SSE response
    Sidecar-->>EnvoyGW: Streaming response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Encoder: Flow 3: Encoder/Prefill/Decode Multimodal (Sidecar E/P/D)
    EnvoyGW->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(multimodal content)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Note over Sidecar: Validate encoder + prefill targets<br/>against SSRF allowlist
    Sidecar->>Encoder: POST encode request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    Encoder-->>Sidecar: Encoded embeddings + KV params
    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/completions<br/>with encoded context<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill result + KV cache params
    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/completions<br/>with KV cache reference<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming SSE response
    Sidecar-->>EnvoyGW: Streaming response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+
